.IP "\fBGO gc\fP - gpiochip open device"
.IP "" 4

.br
This is a privileged command.  See \fBpermits\fP.

.br
This command opens a gpiochip.

.br

\fBExample\fP
.br

.EX
$ rgs c 1 go 0 # open /dev/gpiochip0
.br
