.IP "\fBGSGF h g\fP - GPIO group free"
.IP "" 4

.br
This command releases the group of GPIO identified by the group
leader \fBg\fP.  The GPIO
may now be claimed by another user or for a different purpose.

.br

\fBExample\fP
.br

.EX
rgs c 1 gsgf 1 22
.br

.EE

